event.abstract:
 Innovate UK is the UK's innovation agency,. We fund and support UK entrepeneurs to grow and scale up in the UK.

Open RAN (Radio Access Network) movement is a new approach to building mobile networks. It has been supported through the government’s Diversification Strategy and was backed by £250 million to invest in the Open Networks R&D Fund. Innovate UK is helping the government to deliver a&nbsp;£70m Future Telecoms Technology Mission Fund launched on 5th October 2023. Innovate UK is focussing on industry led R&D and is looking to fund innovative projects in Open RAN.&nbsp;

Come and hear about funding opportunities and support available.

