 Discover how the National Digital Twin Programme's Integration Architecture is transforming data sharing across organisations. Our open-source, distributed system enables secure information exchange, guided by robust legal and security frameworks.
&nbsp;
Learn about how we plan to manage data quality and access in a Zero Trust environment, and how we ensure the right information reaches the right people at the right time.
&nbsp;
Join us at OpenUK for a session where we will talk about current achievements, our plans for the future, and our first public release.

